Algorithm for students exam seating arrangement


Start

Step 1: When ever the student enters, first start the student from the left side of the first row of the table
Step 2: and let  one of the Physics student sit there
Step 3: Place a maths student to the left of physics student who initially sat 
Step 4: Place a chemistry student behind the first physics student 
Step 5: Place a physics student behind the maths student 
Step 6: Repeat from step 3 to step 6 to the right until all the students are seated properly

End
